The MPDRP protocol presents a decisive step in Field-aligned medicine—bypassing the genetic and biochemical layers to restore health at the foundational oscillatory level. As QRFT-based diagnostics and phase-field emitters evolve, this method holds the potential to eliminate Stage IV malignancies overnight.

